The paper deals with the problem of planning a closed walk for a UAV to persistently monitor a finite number of stationary targets with dynamically changing properties. This problem involves optimization, robotics, artificial intelligence, and control systems. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.RO (Robotics), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for target classification, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and computer vision techniques for target detection, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
